    <h2>Mission Statment</h2>

    <div class= "mission-statement-text">
        <p>Accuracy Accounting is based in Atlanta, Georgia and was formed in 2018 under the goal of providing a full spectrum of accounting services. Our mission is to provide quality accounting to our clients with our guarantee to an efficient, confidential, and flexible service. </p>
